IRS990.ActivityOrMissionDesc: GLENNON HOSPITAL GUILD'S MAIN PURPOSE IS TO RAISE MONEY FOR SSM CARDINAL GLENNON CHILDREN'S HOSPITAL, AN ORGANIZATION DESCRIBED IN IRC SECTION 170(B)(1)(A)(III).
IRS990.MissionDesc: THROUGH OUR EXCEPTIONAL HEALTH CARE SERVICES, WE REVEAL THE HEALING PRESENCE OF GOD.
IRS990.Desc: DURING FISCAL YEAR 2017, GLENNON HOSPITAL GUILD CONTRIBUTED OVER $54,000 TO THE CARDINAL GLENNON CHILDREN'S FOUNDATION, WHICH SUPPORTS HOSPITAL OPERATIONS AT SSM HEALTH CARDINAL GLENNON CHILDREN'S HOSPITAL, INCLUDING SUPPORT FOR NEW HOSPITAL MEDICAL EQUIPMENT.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: Form 990, Part VI, Line 11b Review of form 990 by governing body
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: EXECUTIVE BOARD MEMBERS PROVIDE FORM 990 INFORMATION TO THE TAX DEPARTMENT OF SSM HEALTH. WHILE UNRELATED TO THE GLENNON HOSPITAL GUILD, SSM HEALTH IS AN AFFILIATE OF THE CARDINAL GLENNON CHILDREN'S FOUNDATION, THE PRIMARY BENEFICIARY OF THE GLENNON HOSPITAL GUILD. ALL THREE ORGANIZATIONS ARE TAX EXEMPT UNDER IRC SECTION 501(C)(3). THE SSM HEALTH TAX DEPARTMENT PREPARES THE FORM 990 AND PROVIDES THE RETURN TO THE GUILD TREASURER FOR APPROVAL PRIOR TO FILING. A COMPLETE COPY OF THE FORM IS PROVIDED TO THE BOARD MEMBERS OF THE GLENNON HOSPITAL GUILD AT THE NEXT REGULARLY SCHEDULED BOARD MEETING.
